getRangeBottom

public double getRangeBottom()
The client can optionally specify its own range bottom and top, which will be used by the RangeAxis to override the actual min/max range values contained in the Dataset. Should be set in conjunction with getRangeTop().

getRangeTop

public double getRangeTop()
The client can optionally specify its own range bottom and top, which will be used by the RangeAxis to override the actual min/max range values contained in the Dataset. Should be set in conjunction with getRangeBottom().
